===================
backlight-indicator
===================

Adjusts a laptop's backlight automatically, by using camera samples taken at a user definable interval. Also you can set backlight at desired level (from 0 to 100) easily from your panel.

============
Requirements
============

Required dependencies:

    gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
    gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0,
    gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1,
    gir1.2-notify-0.7,
    gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0,
    gir1.2-gst-plugins-base-1.0

========
Download
========

Download the package:

    $ git clone https://github.com/atareao/backlight-indicator

=======
Install
=======

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:atareao/backlight-indicator
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install backlight-indicator
